e="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">妈妈回答说，去看你自己的内心，答案在那里。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">QIQI选的绘本教会我们:</strong></span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">不管你现实生活中有没有住着宫殿，有上百个仆人和士兵。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red;">公主也未必只是你们平时看到的童话故事那样。其实，我们未必要羡慕公主的生活，每一个女孩都是独特的，最重要的是自信。</span></span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 1em auto; padding: 5px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: nowrap; overflow-x: scroll;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appdVgl9ota6006/image/ueditor/68384500_1554857614.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8kibhtyr5ag8sufmqhmbub5gc2ibkg4j2ibtcktgpyayicny2bdae9tostxverurdl9li6lxkupjqnyzo09goztldw/640" title="公主封面.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline-block;"/><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appdVgl9ota6006/image/ueditor/79318500_1554857614.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8kibhtyr5ag8sufmqhmbub5gc2ibkg4j2ibyaejttogm17icety5jeichr2c7wdrynz0lcyqciblq9y8cauahblfvyna/640" title="第二期第4夜Do Princesses Wear Hiking Boots_页面_05.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline-block;"/><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appdVgl9ota6006/image/ueditor/92550400_1554857614.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8kibhtyr5ag8sufmqhmbub5gc2ibkg4j2ibwfpayo4uxwgqbib7kzq1hormefyhmd8qfcpzqtxjbw0x3zeqnfu22uq/640" title="第二期第4夜Do Princesses