 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 556.296px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 54px; font-weight: bold; -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgb(168, 168, 168); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="autonum" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">2</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">.</span></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(168, 168, 168); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(168, 168, 168); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 1em 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1em 4px 2px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(168, 168, 168); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1em 4px 2px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(168, 168, 168); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65);">She Made a Monster</span></strong></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1em 4px 2px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(168, 168, 168); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">（NO.171）</span></section><section style="margin: 1em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">著名的玛丽小姐，诗人雪莱的夫人，独自一人开启了西方乃至整个人类的科幻世界，她创造了一个怪物。她为那个创造怪物的疯狂科学家起名为弗兰克斯坦。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">这本绘本，讲述了玛丽创作科学怪人的始末，玛丽雪莱创造了一些新的东西，这是一种新的故事形式，今天我们叫它科幻小说。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65);">QIQI选的绘本教会我们:</span></strong>&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">玛丽雪莱，她开启了西方科幻小说这一新的文学类型。科学和文艺界还有许多了不起的女性，各种原因，没被大众所熟知。我们应尽力将世界的多样性展示给孩子，让他们获得前行的力量。</span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 1em auto; padding: 5px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: nowrap; overflow-x: sc