需一套教材（1-182课）”的第30课、第171课，还有两本即将在26夜第八期（184课、198课）中呈现。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></strong></section></section><section style="margin: -20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-bottom: 20px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); border-left: 20px solid transparent; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; width: 35px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appdVgl9ota6006/image/ueditor/61377500_1554857613.cn/mmbiz_gif/8kibhtyr5ag8sufmqhmbub5gc2ibkg4j2ib3icoqkxxkzp7sueddfx275y8uxpfxdspuyjnaowvrbh8br92of61bva/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; width: 34.9884px; display: block;"/><br/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><br/><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; text-align: left;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 40px; display: inline-block;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appdVgl9ota6006/image/ueditor/52145700_1554857614.cn/mmbiz_gif/8ki